      public static HttpRequestMethod.Properties newRequestMethodProperties(boolean safe, boolean idempotent, boolean cacheable)
      Create a new HttpRequestMethod.Properties object for specified safe, idempotent, and cacheable. Generally, the constants in HttpRequestMethod.Properties should be used.
      Parameters:

      idempotent - true if a idempotent method
